{"search_data": "CentralPradhan Mantri Awas Yojana Online Applications for UP & Punjab Disabled TemporarilyUnder the PMAY-U, the central government is providing financial assistance to the urban poor of the country to own a home. The financial assistance is provided under different components including direct benefit transfer and subsidy on home loan. The central government aims to provide homes to about 2 Crore families in urban India by the year 2022.Prime Minister of India, Shri Narendra Modi has recently announced some amendments in the PMAY home loan scheme. As per the new announcement, the eligible beneficiaries can now avail a home loan of up to Rs. 12 Lakh for a period of up to 20 years against Rs. 6.5 Lakh for 15 years as per the previous guidelines.The central government has now also introduced the Middle Income Group of the society to the scheme and avail loan benefits. A home loan availed under Pradhan Matri Awas Yojana to buy the first home will save about Rs. 2.4 Lakh to the borrower through the interest subsidy being provided by the government.For detailed information about PMAY-U online applications, use the links below:Apply Online for Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana (PMAY)\u092a\u094d\u0930\u0927\u093e\u0928\u092e\u0902\u0924\u094d\u0930\u0940 \u0906\u0935\u093e\u0938 \u092f\u094b\u091c\u0928\u093e \u0915\u0947 \u0932\u093f\u090f \u0911\u0928\u0932\u093e\u0907\u0928 \u0906\u0935\u0947\u0926\u0928 \u0915\u0948\u0938\u0947 \u0915\u0930\u0947\u0902 \u2013 \u092a\u0942\u0930\u0940 \u091c\u093e\u0928\u0915\u093e\u0930\u0940   Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now  at  "}